'''Shield X''' was an experimental [[Galactic Empire/Legends|Imperial]] [[Deflector shield generator/Legends|deflector shield generator]] that afforded any [[Starship/Legends|starship]] powered by it near-invulnerability against standard attacks.

It was stolen by the [[Alliance to Restore the Republic/Legends|Alliance to Restore the Republic]] during the [[Galactic Civil War/Legends|Galactic Civil War]]. The [[CR90 corvette/Legends|CR90 corvette]] [[Ram's Head|''Blade 5'']] (later captured as ''[[Ram's Head]]'') was outfitted with the device, and used during [[Operation Ram's Head]]. Its usage following that operation remains undocumented.

Some time later the Empire attempted to recreate the technology at a secret space installation. The base was destroyed by a Rebel [[A/SF-01 B-wing starfighter/Legends|B-wing]] strike force, and the project was supposedly stopped for good.

